Additional terms and clarifications

AI assistant prompt text
------------------------

Prompt text loaded at deploy time — via `AGENT_PRIMING_PROMPT_FILE`,
`AGENT_INSTRUCTIONS_FILE`, or equivalent file-based configuration — is
**deployment configuration**, not part of the Program source code under AGPL.

Operators may bring their own prompts and keep them private. Custom prompt text is not
considered a modification of this Program merely because it is mounted or referenced at
runtime. Operators are not required to publish custom prompts when they have not
otherwise modified and conveyed Corresponding Source for this Program.

Reference prompts shipped in `prompts/` in this repository are defaults for convenience
only. Replacing them at deploy time does not, by itself, trigger a source-distribution
obligation for those replacements.
